name: Rainbow-dash.tmbundle
tagline: A bright and colorful syntax highlighting theme for TextMate based on “Mac Classic” by Chris Thomas.
body:
# Rainbow Dash — TextMate Theme

This bundle contains a bright and colorful theme for [TextMate](https://github.com/textmate/textmate). It is based on “Mac Classic” by Chris Thomas.

![Preview image for the Rainbow Dash TextMate theme](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sanssecours/Rainbow-Dash.tmbundle/master/Documentation/Preview.png)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
